DEPENDENCIES

libtiff must be installed on this machine before you can compile Panda. 
libtiff is available from http://www.freshmeat.net -- do a search for it...

INSTALLATION

Type "make all" to build a demo application. Type "make lib" and "make install"
(the last one as root) to install the API.

